<script>
<![CDATA[
--[[
To use this plugin replace the line above starting with Accelerator for as many accelerators as you want to add, for example:

    Accelerator("Shift+s", "frimble This is for shift+s!")
	Accelerator("Shift+r", "frimble This is for shift+r!")
  
And put them in place of the current line.
	
This should load on installing the plugin, however if for whatever reason it doesn't, you can manually type 'add_accelerator' into the command line to add them.
]]--
function OnPluginInstall ()
	ColourNote("orange", "", "Adding accelerators...")
	Execute("add_accelerators")
end
